data.description: Welcome to Sought-After Nostalgic Cherry Pines, Nestled in the Heart of Historic Tomball. This Single-Story Home was Constructed with Energy Efficiency in Mind and Designed to Maximize Space and Functionality with an Open-Concept Split Floor Plan. This Lovely Home Features Modern Finishes and the Open Kitchen Flows into the Dining and Living Area, Bringing Everyone Together. The Home Office Provides a Quiet Work Space or a Play or Craft Room. Primary Suite Offers High Ceilings, Lots of Natural Lighting, Double Sinks, Separate Shower & Walk-In Closet. Enjoy the Spacious Backyard with Wonderful Covered Patio for Relaxing or Entertaining. Minutes from All that the City of Tomball has to Offer; Live Music, Festivals, Nature, Shopping, Restaurants, Museums and More. Convenient Access to the Recently Expanded SH 249 and Grand Parkway. Located in the Highly Sought after Tomball School District and a LOW Tax Rate of 2.2541%
